<strong>Bloodstone Eyepatch - AC 4</strong>
<font size=-1>(<a href="/prices/item/bloodstone_eyepatch.shtml">View Going Price</a>)</font><BR>
Slot: <a href="/armour/face.shtml">Face</a><BR>
Weight: 0.1 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/bard/armour/face.shtml">BRD</a>, <a href="/cleric/armour/face.shtml">CLR</a>, <a href="/druid/armour/face.shtml">DRU</a>, <a href="/monk/armour/face.shtml">MNK</a>, <a href="/paladin/armour/face.shtml">PAL</a>, <a href="/ranger/armour/face.shtml">RNG</a>, <a href="/rogue/armour/face.shtml">ROG</a>, <a href="/shadow_knight/armour/face.shtml">SHD</a>, <a href="/shaman/armour/face.shtml">SHM</a>, <a href="/warrior/armour/face.shtml">WAR</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) <BR>
(AGI +3) (WIS +3) </font>
<BR>
Dropped in Mistmoore.<BR>
<BR>
Avg. Price Overall: 394pp (13 quotes)<BR>
