<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Saavak</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-11 11:59:30</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Ok, you all are wrong.  There are 2 Imp Familiars that spawn in Mistmoore.  There is one that spawns in the Graveyard which drops the Sac. Dagger.  The other spawns in the Courtyard & he is the one who drops the Bloodstone Eyepatch.  He spawned twice in about 30-45min.  I'm not sure if that is normal or our group was just lucky, but it dropped the eyepatch both times.  Hope this information helps out.<BR>
<BR>
Saavak Spiritwind<BR>
Barbarian Shaman of the 35th season</font></td></tr></table>
