<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Sollex</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-28 17:51:25</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I've camped the GraveYard for many  many  many hours, with groups. Usually at the same time we clean out the Jail(3 spawn, behind and to the left of the Crypt, false wall), while waiting for the GY to spawn(5 spawn). Anyway, The Imp is a rare spawn. Any one of the 5 spawns in the GY can be it's place holder. Though Ive only seen it spawn 3 times at 2 different spots in the GY. I really couldnt tell you if anouther Imp spawns somewhere in the castle or not, cause Ive never been in the Castle yet. At lvl 34(war,barb), unless you have a preformed guild,friends,etc. group formed already before you head to MM, its very hard sometimes(weekends the best) to get into a "Pick-up" group. Due to the low numbers of palyers in the zone at any one time.<BR>
 I think its worth 300pp easy. If you dont think it is..  go camp the GY for a few days and see if you get it, I wish you all the Luck in Norrath.<BR>
  Oh yea..inless your grouped with a bunch of Twinks, you have to win the roll on a rare spawn's rare drop.<BR>
<BR>
 Sollex Iceblood, Mercenary <BR>
  ~:34th circle of Power:~</font></td></tr></table>
